SIMPSON v. WARDEN OF MARYLAND PENITENTIARY [App. No. 32,

September Term, 1961.]

Decided November 17, 1961.

Before Bruñe, C. J., and Henderson, Hammond, Prescott, Hornby and Marbury, JJ.

PER Curiam.

Application for leave to appeal from a denial of post conviction relief is denied for the reasons set forth in the opinion of the court below.
